  "title": "Sales Executive",
  "description": "<p><strong>Roles & Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li><p>Develop new account locally and overseas</p></li><li><p>Manage existing account assigned by team leader</p></li><li><p>Provide market information and feedback on customers</p></li><li><p>Visit customers locally and overseas</p></li><li><p>Cross sell all products</p></li><li><p>Prepare weekly report on daily activities</p></li><li><p>Prepare bi-monthly sales pipeline report</p></li><li><p>Work with PIC & team leader on all enquires</p></li><li><p>Contribute to Gas group report</p></li><li><p>Attending to sales enquiries and quotations</p></li><li><p>Source new products for customer’s enquiries</p></li><li><p>Follow up on orders and delivery </p></li><li><p>Country in charge for SSBVN prepare bi-monthly group report & weekly report to discuss with Key account manager.</p></li><li><p>Other ad-hoc duties assigned</p></li></ul><p><strong>Requirements</strong></p><ul><li><p>Minimum diploma in business management, marketing, or related fields</p></li><li><p>At least 3 years of sales experience, with a proven track record of achieving or exceeding sales targets.</p></li><li><p>Strong interpersonal skills and ability to build relationships.</p></li><li><p>Excellent communication and presentation skills.</p></li><li><p>Proactive in identifying and pursuing sales opportunities.</p></li><li><p>Ability to work independently and effectively manage multiple priorities.</p></li><li><p>Proficiency in both Chinese and English</p></li><li><p>Willing to travel overseas</p></li><li><p>Singaporean only may apply</p></li></ul><p><strong>Benefits</strong></p><ul><li><p>Annual Wage Supplement (AWS)</p></li><li><p>Variable Bonus</p></li><li><p>Outpatient Medical </p></li><li><p>Transport Allowance</p></li><li><p>Travel Allowance</p></li></ul><p><br />\n\n</p>",
